COPYRIGHT AND AUTHORSHIP
========================

This package is a performance-optimized fork of the original DDRTree package
(version 0.1.5) from CRAN.

ORIGINAL WORK (DDRTree v0.1.5 and earlier)
-------------------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2015-2017 Xiaojie Qiu, Cole Trapnell, Qi Mao, Li Wang

Original Authors:
  - Xiaojie Qiu <xqiu@uw.edu>
  - Cole Trapnell
  - Qi Mao
  - Li Wang

Original Publication:
  Qi Mao, Li Wang, Steve Goodison, and Yijun Sun (2015).
  "Dimensionality Reduction via Graph Structure Learning."
  The 21st ACM SIGKDD Conference on Knowledge Discovery and Data Mining (KDD'15).
  http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=2783309

Original CRAN Package:
  https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=DDRTree
  Released: 2017-04-30
  Version: 0.1.5

MODIFICATIONS (DDRTree2 v0.2.0)
--------------------------------
Copyright (c) 2025 Billsfriend

Fork Maintainer:
  - Billsfriend <Billsfriend1999@outlook.com>

Modifications Include:
  - OpenMP parallelization for 11x performance improvement
  - Efficient matrix broadcasting optimizations
  - Pre-allocated memory management
  - Build system improvements (Makevars)
  - Comprehensive performance documentation
  - Updated package metadata and documentation

Date of Fork: October 2025
Fork Repository: https://github.com/Billsfriend/DDRTree2

SCOPE OF MODIFICATIONS
-----------------------
The modifications in this fork are limited to:
  1. Performance optimizations (OpenMP parallelization)
  2. Code refactoring for efficiency
  3. Build system improvements
  4. Documentation updates

The core DDRTree algorithm, mathematical formulations, and functionality
remain unchanged from the original work. All modifications maintain
identical numerical results and full backward compatibility.

